subSubSection.paragraph:
Conspicuous cuticle present along the rim. Hemipenis with strongly asymmetrical lobes. Lobes foot-like, but more robust on right than on left Hp. Ejaculatory duct terminated on distal lobe. Three bare setae present near the upper central margin and one small seta called caudal process on between left and right (
Fig. 12B
).

